To effeciently write [[Unit Tests In Python]], one should install these tools:

* `pip install nose`
* `pip install nose-watch` - to run tests continuously
* `pip install rednose` - to colorize the output

Once these tools are installed, one should start a session by typing this in the terminal:

```bash
(base) boris@computer:~$ cd path/to/project
(base) boris@computer:~/path/to/project$ nosetests --with-watch --rednose --nologcapture
```